| Documents | Search Time | Total Time | Accuracy |
|-----------|-------------|------------|----------|
| 1,000 | ~200ms | ~2.5s | 94% |
| 10,000 | ~500ms | ~3.2s | 96% |
| 100,000 | ~800ms | ~4.1s | 97% |

